formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
This Certificate is issued subject to following:
1. We are certifying amount incurred and paid which can be verified from the books of account maintained and not certifying any estimated data.

2. The LLP has filed a project alteration application with Gujarat RERA Authority and the said application for alteration of Savvy Studioz Project was approved by Gujarat RERA Authority on 11/08/2020. All the estimated/projected cost figures shown in the above certificate are as per the Project Alteration application which  is approved by Gujarat RERA Authority. 
 
3.  The land value is arrived on the basis of valuation report obtained from the approved valuer DNP Engineers for the purpose ascertaining market value of land as on 31/03/2017.

4.The details required in the excel sheet for booked and unbooked units are given on the basis of data received from the management and we have verified the details of only amount received from the books of accounts submitted before us. All other details are given on the basis of information received from the management of the LLP.  
5. As per Form 1 and Form 2 submitted, the project is completed and 100% work is finished. The Building use permission is also received. 

6. The certificate in form 3 is given for QPR on 08/06/2022, the same certificate is given for QE. However, for QE, the website requires new UDIN number and hence new UDIN is generated and all other details remain the same as provided in QPR -18 submitted today.
